dmca.title: Temporary Delisting NobleCountyFreecycle (IN)
dmca.body:
Hello moderators,
 
Our trademark people have been working to reach you since April.  Due to the lack of response from your group about trademark requirements your group has been delisted.  This may only be temporary.
 
If you contact them within 48hours of this note we can work together to resolve this problem.  Please email them at trademark1@freecycle.org 
 
Every Freecycle(TM) group is important to us and communication is the key.
 
Thank you,
 
Deron Beal
Founder & Executive Director
The Freecycle Network(TM)
